2911, \"end\": 2917, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quincy_Center_station\", \"score\": 0.9999999943506737, \"rank\": 4.15030895651902e-09, \"text\": \"Quincy\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quincy_Center_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quincy_Center_station\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Can he get there?\", \"from\": 2956, \"to\": 2973, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He does!\", \"from\": 2974, \"to\": 2982, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's gold for the USA!\", \"from\": 2983, \"to\": 3005, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Quincy Hall with the most epic comeback!\", \"from\": 3006, \"to\": 3046, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3006, \"end\": 3012, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quincy_Center_station\", \"score\": 0.9999999943506737, \"rank\": 4.15030895651902e-09, \"text\": \"Quincy\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quincy_Center_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quincy_Center_station\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My goodness!\\\"\", \"from\": 3047, \"to\": 3060, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sanya Richards-Ross on Quincy Hall's comeback win in the men's 400m final: \\\"I have never seen anyone run the 400m like that.\", \"from\": 3062, \"to\": 3186, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3062, \"end\": 3081, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sanya_Richards-Ross\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sanya Richards-Ross\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sanya_Richards-Ross\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sanya_Richards-Ross\"}, {\"begin\": 3085, \"end\": 3091, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quincy_Center_station\", \"score\": 0.9999999943506737, \"rank\": 4.15030895651902e-09, \"text\": \"Quincy\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quincy_Center_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quincy_Center_station\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Around the turn, he looked like he was in a world of hurt.\", \"from\": 3187, \"to\": 3245, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He was grimacing coming off the turn...and then he found something deep...He has that kind of swag and that fearlessness that it takes to be the best 400-meter runner in the world.\\\"\", \"from\": 3246, \"to\": 3427, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kara Goucher on Kenneth Rooks' silver medal in the 3,000m steeplechase: \\\"In only his second global championship, (he) decided he was going to go to the front.\", \"from\": 3429, \"to\": 3587, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3429, \"end\": 3441, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kara_Goucher\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kara Goucher\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kara_Goucher\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kara_Goucher\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He talked about it -- he wanted a race that ramped up, he wanted to have something left in his legs in that final bit, and boy, did he have something left\\u2026the American distance team is just momentum after momentum.\\\"\", \"from\": 3588, \"to\": 3803, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3747, \"end\": 3755, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.6214527160860467, \"rank\": 0.6091310554023203, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Diffey on Rooks: \\\"Kenneth Rooks is resilient!\", \"from\": 3805, \"to\": 3850, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He's racing for that silver...Team USA medals with authority!\", \"from\": 3851, \"to\": 3912, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Unbelievable!\\\"\", \"from\": 3913, \"to\": 3927, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Goucher on Rooks: \\\"[American record holder]Evan Jagercarried this event for so long.Kenneth Rooksis the next American superstar in the steeplechase.\\\"\", \"from\": 3929, \"to\": 4078, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3949, \"end\": 3957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.6214527160860467, \"rank\": 0.6091310554023203, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 4038, \"end\": 4046, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.6214527160860467, \"rank\": 0.6091310554023203, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Television_in_the_United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ato Boldon on Noah Lyles finishing second in his 200m semifinal: \\\"It's a good time to remind you that in the 100m dash here, Noah did not win his heat nor his semifinal, and we know how the final went.\", \"from\": 4080, \"to\": 4281, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4080, \"end\": 4090, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ato_Boldon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.039031305872857e-20, \"text\": \"Ato Boldon\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ato_Boldon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ato_Boldon\"}, {\"begin\": 4094, \"end\": 4104, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He clearly was content to be in second place.\\\"\", \"from\": 4282, \"to\": 4328, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Diffey on 400m hurdles U.S. record holder Rai Benjamin: \\\"He is in scintillating form this year.\", \"from\": 4330, \"to\": 4425, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4372, \"end\": 4384, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rai_Benjamin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rai Benjamin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rai_Benjamin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rai_Benjamin\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As the old saying goes, it is so difficult to peak at the right time, meaning the Olympic Games, but it seems that Rai has hit that form.\\\"\", \"from\": 4426, \"to\": 4564, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Boldon on the upcoming rematch between Benjamin and reigning gold medalist Karsten Warholm in the men's 400m hurdles: \\\"We need to be very clear about this: this event produced the best event of the Tokyo Olympics.\", \"from\": 4566, \"to\": 4779, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4605, \"end\": 4613, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin\", \"score\": 0.8089506085646905, \"rank\": 0.23094991832127584, \"text\": \"Benjamin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Benjamin\"}, {\"begin\": 4641, \"end\": 4656, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karsten_Warholm\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Karsten Warholm\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karsten_Warholm\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karsten_Warholm\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The way Rai Benjamin looks and Karsten Warholm looks, we may be looking at a repeat here in Paris.\", \"from\": 4780, \"to\": 4878, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4788, \"end\": 4800, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rai_Benjamin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rai Benjamin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rai_Benjamin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rai_Benjamin\"}, {\"begin\": 4811, \"end\": 4826, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karsten_Warholm\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Karsten Warholm\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karsten_Warholm\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karsten_Warholm\"}, {\"begin\": 4872, \"end\": 4877, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.557729936446962e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This just is not something we are used to seeing.\", \"from\": 4879, \"to\": 4928, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You are not supposed to run 48.78 and take essentially half of the race off like Rai just did.\", \"from\": 4929, \"to\": 5023, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Phenomenal.\\\"\", \"from\": 5024, \"to\": 5036, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Diffey on Snoop Dogg watching the men's 200m semifinals with Noah Lyles' mom: \\\"I think Snoop Dogg has been seen more at these events than the actual Olympic mascot.\\\"\", \"from\": 5038, \"to\": 5203, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5048, \"end\": 5058, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Snoop Dogg\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\"}, {\"begin\": 5099, \"end\": 5109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 5125, \"end\": 5135, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.or